Domain: coinmarketcap.com

Description: Content Security Policy is missing critical directives

Detected: 2025-04-20 00:26:11

Risk Assessment

CVSS Score: 5.8

CVSS Vector: CVSS:3.1/AV:N/AC:L/PR:L/UI:R/S:U/C:L/I:L/A:L

CWE Information

CWE-693: Protection Mechanism Failure

Learn more about this vulnerability type

Exploit Scenario

This vulnerability could potentially be exploited by malicious actors.

Impact

This vulnerability has a moderate impact and could lead to limited data exposure or functionality disruption.

Remediation Guidance

Implement proper input validation and output encoding.

Technical Details

csp: frame-ancestors 'self' https://ss.datasconsole.com;

missing_directives: ['default-src', 'script-src', 'object-src', 'style-src', 'img-src', 'media-src', 'frame-src', 'font-src', 'connect-src', 'form-action']

recommendation: Add missing directives, especially default-src, script-src, and object-src
